==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gunboat
<hw>Gun"boat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Nav.)</fld> <def>A vessel of light draught, carrying one or more
guns, used for operations in shallow waters.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Nav.)</fld> <def>Any small naval vessel carrying
mounted guns.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Guncotton</ent>⟦br⟧
